org.framed.orm.model

Interface Rolemodel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Container, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    RolemodelImpl

    public interface Rolemodel
extends Container
    A representation of the model object 'Rolemodel'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Subcontexts
    • Participants
    • Players
    • Compartment
    • Parent Group
    • Groups

    See Also:
    OrmPackage.getRolemodel()
